title: Authorizes municipalities to enter into contracts to sell delinquent real property tax liens to private parties
summary: Authorizes municipalities to, on or before December 31, 2011, enter into contracts to sell delinquent real property tax liens to private parties.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the real property tax law, in relation to authorizing any municipality to enter into a contract to sell some or all of the delinquent tax liens held by such municipality to a private party; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon the expiration thereof
